{"id": 2026, "genre": 1001, "title": "说起来，你受不了火车站的哪些设计？", "description": "外观是不是宏伟壮观我并不太 care，就问能给候车厅多添几个椅子吗？（题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 4506, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171122121444veWzyjT8ZmgBpiUd.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-23T03:00:45Z", "options": [{"id": 250624, "content": "郑州东站高铁站只开一个地铁口，光排队进地铁站花了一个半小时。恶心，丢人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191621}, {"id": 250880, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1184453}, {"id": 252416, "content": "我什么火车没有里程积分？我什么没有特价票？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475247}, {"id": 251912, "content": "想起上海火车站出站口 有个地方没电梯还特别高 那次拎着30斤的行李回家 爬一半就想躺地上哭了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199181}, {"id": 254728, "content": "有电梯不开", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086674}, {"id": 250889, "content": "最恨：车站远在天边，广场宽广无边，停车通道全满，安检动线智障，走廊深不到底，厕所全看缘分，餐饮上蹿下跳，广播浑浊不清，取票犹如健身，闸机好坏无常，候车空调看脸，站台挡雨看天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 69552}, {"id": 250890, "content": "站着坐着一个价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192697}, {"id": 250635, "content": "西安火车站，很想吐槽，有次去玩，结果下暴雨，陇海线停运，滞留人口那真叫爆棚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1169579}, {"id": 250892, "content": "这", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1184453}, {"id": 251916, "content": "空间太狭窄，买站票的人没地方站?，有人来就让让让。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114139}, {"id": 250637, "content": "不得不提提济南火车站，往年的风光", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1169579}, {"id": 250638, "content": "重庆的举手??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729146}, {"id": 250639, "content": "实名制和安检时间过长", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147749}, {"id": 250895, "content": "体育竞技", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173913}, {"id": 250640, "content": "车站里的矿泉水和泡面为什么买那么贵！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138453}, {"id": 250896, "content": "密集恐惧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173913}, {"id": 250897, "content": "哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173913}, {"id": 252694, "content": "行李没有地方放", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173225}, {"id": 250647, "content": "上面那个南广场北广场的是不是重庆的，哈哈哈，重庆北站南广场北广场。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607970}, {"id": 250649, "content": "小商小铺能不能少点？别那么low", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143922}, {"id": 252697, "content": "能不能把通风加强一点？火车上还不够臭嘛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1204134}, {"id": 250651, "content": "哪里的受不了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777364}, {"id": 250652, "content": "厕所厕所厕所！！！请增加厕所数量并且尽量保持卫生", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 251676, "content": "反正我每次去火车站都找不到站台的，都是跟着别人走的！为什么没有人引导一下你。???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198375}, {"id": 250653, "content": "我们印度哪里都好，尤其是火车，绝对是世界上领先的，我没什么意见，就是想说，火车车顶上的人能不能不要总敲车顶，声音每次都震得我耳朵疼！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164311}, {"id": 250654, "content": "杭州东站还不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191722}, {"id": 251425, "content": "没有地方坐啊 导致每次坐火车都是掐点到的火车站", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197416}, {"id": 252453, "content": "一：应该整一个大一点的书吧，供游客利用闲暇时间去阅读，而非抱手机！二：多一些手机充电且安全存放设备。三：增设行李箱储存箱，这样就可以不用提着箱子去吃饭去买东西了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202960}, {"id": 251177, "content": "上海南站 每次在那里坐校车都会迷路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697102}, {"id": 252202, "content": "重庆北站", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195247}, {"id": 252714, "content": "卧铺！ 上中下  上铺究竟是怎么生存下去的！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1204183}, {"id": 253226, "content": "火车站都还好，深圳机场设计是真受不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401817}, {"id": 252971, "content": "检票口离乘车口真的太远了，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205709}, {"id": 250926, "content": "卧铺的走廊真的超级挤，晚上不开灯根本找不到位置。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802667}, {"id": 251185, "content": "不是说是世界上最先进的动车吗？为什么空调永远是夏天必须穿外套，冬天又不能脱外套，既然这么冷，干嘛不搞成敞篷列车，省钱省电省材料，还特别拉轰", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1184442}, {"id": 258354, "content": "重庆北站，奇葩中的战斗机…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1232094}, {"id": 250932, "content": "只想对下面某个回答说  大叔大妈不会买票也挺正常的啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846695}, {"id": 250934, "content": "北京火车站那陈旧的老年设计，完全无法应对如今的客流量", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 877242}, {"id": 250682, "content": "广州南站的快捷换乘，有电梯也不开，有时候换乘时间本来就很紧张，还要提着行李爬一长段楼梯…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191762}, {"id": 250938, "content": "搬着那么重的行李，上上下下那么多楼梯，弯弯绕绕的，坐了这么多次如果让我自己找路还是找不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936637}, {"id": 250683, "content": "狭小的过道环境。举例两个：不合时宜的叫卖，过道挤得满满的，一辆车子过来，开一条道并没有那么容易；还有行李，稍微人多点，就没地方放，堆挤在过道上", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986568}, {"id": 253500, "content": "上下楼拖着行李箱没有电梯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208851}, {"id": 255804, "content": "福州交通太差了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219371}, {"id": 250946, "content": "整个车站规划太乱，进站直接找不着北，接人更难找，武昌火车站去一次迷路一次……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192994}, {"id": 250948, "content": "红烧牛肉面味蔓延的恐惧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155587}, {"id": 253509, "content": "到处都找不到钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747504}, {"id": 253510, "content": "进站能不能不要安检，浪费时间和人力，实际达到的效果微乎其微", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747504}, {"id": 250696, "content": "广州东站换乘广州站，乘渡路线还能再长点吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190747}, {"id": 250954, "content": "永远无法理解为什么中国的厕所会那么脏，到越南的时候印象最深刻的就是厕所干净。长途卧铺车上都会配有坐便器，再加标配水枪，我国这一点真的不行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1193028}, {"id": 252746, "content": "排队！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140092}]}